            <p>Dear
{!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Contact__c},</p>
            <p>Congratulations on your new SunPower Solar System Lease! We want to hear all about your experience, and hope you can take this <a href="http://survey.sunpowercorp.com/go?iv=3ls95x2ymjv8u&q1={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Account1Id__c}&q2={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.ContactId__c}&q3={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Primary_Contact_Email__c}&q4={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Opportunity_IDId__c}&q5={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Partner_AccountId__c}&q6={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Opportunity_Record_Type__c}&q7={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Survey_Response_Date__c}&q8={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Survey_Link__c}"
