to let us know!<br>
            </p>
            <p> </p>
            <p>We are excited that you chose SunPower to help meet your energy needs. We know you have many choices for home solar systems, and appreciate your business. We recognize the importance of a strong partnership with our leasing customers over the years ahead. Critical to our ability to be a strong partner is to have an ongoing dialog on how things are going. Now that the installation is completed, we invite you to tell us about your experience with us and our Dealer, {!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Partner_Account__c}. Your feedback will help us continue to refine our services and Partner programs with the goal of providing you the best customer experience.  </p>
            <p> </p>
            <p>Please take this
short 5 to 10 minute <a href="http://survey.sunpowercorp.com/go?iv=3ls95x2ymjv8u&q1={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Account1Id__c}&q2={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.ContactId__c}&q3={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Primary_Contact_Email__c}&q4={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Opportunity_IDId__c}&q5={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Partner_AccountId__c}&q6={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Opportunity_Record_Type__c}&q7={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Survey_Response_Date__c}&q8={!Customer_Survey_Result__c.Survey_Link__c}"
